Product Details

Description

Features of Feed Buddy Automatic Cricket Bowling Machine -

* Accurate feeding for Hours to perfect your different shots

* Powered by (4 X D Batteries) for usage anywhere

* Usable with tennis balls, sponge balls or light bowling machine balls.

* Ball feeder for stacking 10 balls that shoot out every 5 seconds

* Gentle feed that travels 3-4 m every time

* Four Settings for Closer or longer feed

* Appropriate for all age groupsThis machine is useful for players looking for gentle feeds of balls to develop or improve their skill set and not for the players looking for higher speeds. 

 

At Cricketer Shop, we have the entire range of Cricket Training Equipments.
